Dr. Joseph Odirichukwu Ugboaja, has been named the new Acting Chief Medical Director, Nnamdi Azikiwe University Teaching Hospital (NAUTH) Nnewi,Anambra State.
His appointment was contained in a letter by the Governing Board of the teaching hospital which said he should resume work with effect from January 25.
